{"TopicId":196687,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Forum brightness?","CreatedByName":"alberro\u002B","CreatedById":199496,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T13:22:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"alberro\u002B","CreatedById":199496,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T13:22:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027d be cool to have some sort of dark mode for the forum page. It gets really taxing, since i\u0027ve got some eyesight issues, and it makes it hard to look at very bright screens.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T13:29:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to Kerbal Network, as it\u0027s a suggestion for the forum and not the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought there was a thread on this already to merge into, but I can\u0027t seem to find it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI seem to recall that there\u0027s a browser add-on out there that lets you change sites\u0027 CSS styling and that there\u0027s a profile that give the forum a dark mode.\u00A0 Hopefully someone will chime in with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"alberro\u002B","CreatedById":199496,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T13:31:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223848416\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196687\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221599139794\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to Kerbal Network, as it\u0027s a suggestion for the forum and not the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought there was a thread on this already to merge into, but I can\u0027t seem to find it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI seem to recall that there\u0027s a browser add-on out there that lets you change sites\u0027 CSS styling and that there\u0027s a profile that give the forum a dark mode.\u00A0 Hopefully someone will chime in with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for telling me, i\u0027ll look into it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cattette","CreatedById":206142,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T13:54:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223848416\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196687\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221599139794\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI seem to recall that there\u0027s a browser add-on out there that lets you change sites\u0027 CSS styling and that there\u0027s a profile that give the forum a dark mode.\u00A0 Hopefully someone will chime in with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that would be stylish/userstyles. It has versions for both Chrome and Firefox.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T14:17:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223848413\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196687\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=