\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eus\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E add-on, over Styl\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eish\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E ... Stylish seems to have sold out, to providing and selling user data... Hence, why someone made the Stylus fork from it, minus the user data mining...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nHmm.. I see I really NEED to update my own readme file, to reflect that... \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSince its basically a clone of the original add-on, just without the privacy issues, it also is compatable with all the Userstyles themes.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/openstyles/stylus\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/openstyles/stylus\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-09-03T17:57:49Z\u0022 title=\u002209/03/2020 05:57  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 3, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-03T15:32:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223848470\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196687\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221599146227\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, i HIGHLY recommend using the Styl\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eus\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E add-on, over Styl\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eish\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah... Thanks for that. I thought something rotten was going on with stylish, confirmation is good. Guess it\u0027s safe to reinstall your theme again now, it\u0027s been a while.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-04T13:02:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E, If you\u0027re up for it, starting a thread on that, a la add-on release style, we might be able to find a permanent home for it somewhere....\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}